      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/cdc98d/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2023-09-25T11:47:35.102Z",
      "cooked": "<p>This weekend I had a bit of a \u201chickup\u201d.  It\u2019s my fault what happened, but it\u2019s a bit annoying.<br>\nI did a Zone2 HR mode ride.  After 45 minutes, I wanted to do some HIIT blocks.<br>\nSo I had to put the app first in ERG mode, before I could add a workout.  OK, so I got that working.  I have to admit I was \u201ctoast\u201d after the intervals.  I wanted to get back to HR mode and do a nice cooldown.  But that was not possible.  Since I was \u201ctoast\u201d, I clicked too fast and basically lost my activity\u2026  Again : it was my fault.<br>\nBut : is it hard to make it possible to switch from ERG mode to HR mode and the other way round?</p>",
