      "cooked": "<p>No worries, the mistake was entirely mine.  Human error <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"> After 8 intervals at 150% FTP I clearly didn\u2019t read the red text correctly <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/wink.png?v=9\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wink:\"> Hence my question to make it easier if possible.</p>",
