      "cooked": "<p>Sounds like you need an automated Mixed Mode Structured Workout</p>\n<p>HR + ERG or HR + SLOPE + ERG</p>\n<p>this way, it\u2019s hands free and no red text to click.<br>\nBut this would involve up front plannng tho.</p>",
