    {
      "id": 33304,
      "name": "",
      "username": "Alex",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2023-09-26T06:32:15.575Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes, this is actually the behavior I like to support as well.  From a feature standpoint, I like to do what people want, but I also like to inject my own beliefs a bit <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"></p>\n<p>Even though we are the biggest ERG platform, I totally think people should train more by feel (and no that does not mean chasing every rabbit passes you bye\u2026).  So feel can include some slope, some hr mode and some ERG\u2026   So I prefer to do your request first (which is also easier), and then move to automatic HR mode.</p>",
