      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/57b2e6/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2023-10-26T17:24:00.644Z",
      "cooked": "<p>The HR target has no place in any workout with intervals. HR lags too much.<br>\nIt does work perfectly fine for a steady state workout in my experience. Keeps me nicely just under AeT for at least 90 min without the need to check my display every couple of seconds.<br>\nKeep it simple, use HR for steady state and ERG for interval workouts. Use slope mode for less predictable short intervals.</p>",
